        "## which equals"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "S6hnLqv-7W52"
      },
      "source": [
        "$$\\left[1 - \\frac{x^2}{\\pi^2} \\left(\\frac{1}{1} + \\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{1}{9} + \\frac{1}{16} + \\cdots \\right)\\right] + \\mbox{stuff}$$"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0Z_yGvbT_x2M"
      },
      "source": [
        "## and therefore"
      ]
    },
