      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "uhWJ_gDv7etz"
      },
      "source": [
        "$$1 - \\frac{x^2}{6} = 1 - \\frac{x^2}{\\pi^2} \\left(\\frac{1}{1} + \\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{1}{9} + \\frac{1}{16} + \\cdots \\right)$$"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "R1fZFubR_1RD"
      },
      "source": [
        "## and hence"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
